{"title":"“快乐丸”","authors":["天马　江有生"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":3,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“快乐丸”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马诗　江有生画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李老君的仙丹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观世音的甘泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神话里灵丹妙药千百件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比不上美国的膏丹丸散。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这药名儿却也新鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫什么“兴奋片”、“快乐丸”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报纸广告吹得天花乱坠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说是医诸般绝症怪灵验："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被压迫的人吃了少烦恼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失业的人吃了心情好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既能解忧又会消愁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神通广大真奥妙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失业的人失意的生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的忧愁病者特别多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家争着把药买，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"利润把资本家的钱袋胀破。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骗人的把戏越变越新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资本家的心肠越来越狠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃药消愁愁更愁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的苦难更重更深！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}